  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix the fettuccini pasta with unsweetened applesauce, coconut milk, shredded coconut, ginger paste, vanilla extract, cinnamon powder, and cocoa powder.",
    "Fold in the pumpkin puree until well combined.",
    "Divide the mixture into small portions and shape them into balls or logs for easier frying.",
    "Place each portion on a wire rack lined with parchment paper and air fry for about 12-15 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Once done, serve warm as a side dish or main course."
